# PHASE 3B: Vault + Formulation Detail + Search

## Context
Phase 3A built PractitionerView.jsx with sidebar and dashboard. The vault and other sub-views show "Coming in next phase" placeholders.

## What to build
Edit src/views/PractitionerView.jsx to add the Vault sub-view and the Formulation Detail view.

## Vault sub-view (subView === 'vault')

### Search bar
Flex row, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) bg, border rgba(255,255,255,0.08), 10px radius, 10px 16px padding, margin-bottom 16px.
- 🔍 icon (14px, rgba(255,255,255,0.2))
- Input: flex 1, no bg, no border, no outline, rgba(255,255,255,0.7) text, 14px, placeholder "Search medicines..."
- Use a local state: `const [vaultSearch, setVaultSearch] = useState('');`
- Filter FORMULATIONS: split search into words, match any word against name, conditions, ingredient local/english/botanical names (case insensitive)
- Show count: "{filtered.length} formulations" or "{filtered.length} results for '{vaultSearch}'"

### Formulation cards
Map filtered formulations. Each card:
- rgba(255,255,255,0.03) bg, border rgba(255,255,255,0.06), 14px radius, 20px padding, cursor pointer
- Hover: border brightens to rgba(255,255,255,0.1)
- Name (14px, 500 weight)
- Condition tags: row of pills (inline-block, padding 2px 8px, 4px radius, 10px font, bold, bg rgba(27,107,58,0.12), color #4ADE80)
- "{ingredients.length} ingredients" (11px muted)
- Effectiveness badge: "{effectiveness}%" (bold, green if >=80, gold if >=70, else muted)
- Privacy badge: "🔒 Private" (11px muted)
- onClick: `setSelectedFormulation(f.id)`

Below the real 6 formulations, show 5 ghost cards:
